				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/D%C4%A9nh-Ch%C3%A2u-l%C3%A3o-%C3%B4ng-ca/poem-sMaN29nfwosLLi7BpB4dYg">Dĩnh Châu lão ông ca - 穎州老翁歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/N%E1%BA%A1p-T%C3%A2n/author-0SVWGWsIUnN7yr-6nBm82Q">Nạp Tân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/D%E1%BB%AF-thi-h%E1%BB%AFu-Phan-Long-Tr%C3%A2n-du-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1c-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A2n/poem-c66Lkci6txOArDMiGj9TPw">Dữ thi hữu Phan Long Trân du Côn Sơn nhân tác Côn Sơn hành vân - 與詩友潘龍珍遊崑山因作崑山行云</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Ph%C3%BA-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-h%E1%BB%93ng-mai-hoa-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-ruyQXLBi6AE1vcdir5EWnQ">Phú đắc hồng mai hoa kỳ 1 - 賦得紅梅花其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Qu%C3%A1-h%E1%BA%A3i/poem-09JpLCmR417AUaMAlibYlQ">Quá hải - 過海</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-WwDsTB1mrksavELcH5wndg">Quân hành - 軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-th%C6%B0-k%C3%BD/poem-4_3r_tUgn4sXO_w33S1XKA">Tống Cao tam thập ngũ thư ký - 送高三十五書記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BB%91ng-h%C3%A0nh-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-T%C3%B2ng-Chu/poem-X_KwRfTQ1Q0NeKt9WN_8vg">Tống hành nhân Đỗ Tòng Chu - 送行人杜從周</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/T%E1%BB%91ng-th%C3%A1i-h%E1%BB%8Dc-sinh-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%C3%A1n-Anh-quy-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-VAknFIxs0X7yN0JcPzr5kQ">Tống thái học sinh Nguyễn Hán Anh quy Hồng Châu - 送太學生阮漢英歸洪州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/T%E1%BB%A5ng-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1o-h%E1%BB%8Dc/poem-MYRsfdb_7Z2pq0M9vY3juw">Tụng Thánh Tông đạo học - 頌聖宗道學</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/V%C4%A9nh-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%C3%B4ng-tu%E1%BA%A7n-ca-k%E1%BB%B3-07/poem-tG3Z2i2roxxZ6LXhcC1RFg">Vĩnh Vương đông tuần ca kỳ 07 - 永王東巡歌其七</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
